data.description: Quaint and charming Colonial owned by the same family for over 60 years. This property is unique in the fact that it has a commercial office space which has maintained successful dental and medical practices for the entirety of its history. Gorgeous architecture to appreciate and a great home to do business in and also live in. Exposed beams and meticulous woodwork show pride of ownership. Very conveniently located minutes to 95. Home is undergoing many renovations and upgrades. Four large beds, 2 full baths and a garage for 2. Large yard, corner lot. Don't miss out.
